"und ist nicht dazu verpflichtet, die Website zu aktualisieren."
msgstr ""
"This website is provided to you by McMoe's Solutions. The information "
"available through this website about McMoe's Solutions and third parties has "
"been compiled with the utmost care. However, we cannot guarantee the "
"completeness, accuracy, and timeliness of this information. We assume no "
"liability for errors in the contents of this website. McMoe's Solutions may "
"change this website at its own discretion at any time without notice in "
"whole or in part and/or cease its operation, and is under no obligation to "
"update the website."

